# Add pollen

When the user says **add pollen**, **add by-taxon images**, **add kerkvliet images**,
`@add-pollen`, `@add-by-taxon-images`, `@add-kerkvliet-images`, or equivalent, follow
`.cursor/skills/add-pollen/SKILL.md` end-to-end. Do not skip rename, YAML sync,
species page update, or (when the batch touches Kerkvliet)
`inject_pollen_keys_into_key_json.py`.
